  "english": {
    "sections": [
      {
        "key": "statement",
        "title": "Statement",
        "blocks": [
          {
            "kind": "paragraph",
            "text": "Let f (n, k) be the number of integer pairs (a, b) such that:"
          },
          {
            "kind": "bullets",
            "items": [
              "0 ≤ a, b < n."
            ]
          },
          {
            "kind": "bullets",
            "items": [
              "k(a + b) ≡ ab (mod n)."
            ]
          },
          {
            "kind": "paragraph",
            "text": "Given two integers n and m, you need to calculate"
          },
          {
            "kind": "paragraph",
            "text": "m X f (n, k) k=0"
          },
          {
            "kind": "paragraph",
            "text": "Since the answer may be large, output it modulo 998244353."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "key": "input",
        "title": "Input",
        "blocks": [
          {
            "kind": "paragraph",
            "text": "There are multiple test cases. The first line of the input contains an integer T (1 ≤ T ≤ 10⁴ ), indicating the number of test cases. For each test case: The only line contains two integers n and m (1 ≤ n ≤ 1014 , 0 ≤ m < n). It is guaranteed that there are at most 10 test cases with n greater than 108 ."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "key": "output",
        "title": "Output",
        "blocks": [
          {
            "kind": "paragraph",
            "text": "For each test case, output one line containing an integer, indicating the answer modulo 998244353."
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
  },
  "chinese": {
    "sections": [
      {
        "key": "statement",
        "title": "题目描述",
        "blocks": [
          {
            "kind": "paragraph",
            "text": "设 f(n,k) 表示满足以下条件的整数对 (a,b) 的数量："
          },
          {
            "kind": "bullets",
            "items": [
              "0 ≤ a,b < n。"
            ]
          },
          {
            "kind": "bullets",
            "items": [
              "k(a + b) ≡ ab (mod n)。给定两个整数 n 和 m，求∑m f(n,k) k=0由于答案可能很大，请将答案对 998244353 取模后输出。"
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "key": "input",
        "title": "输入格式",
        "blocks": [
          {
            "kind": "paragraph",
            "text": "有多组测试数据。第一行输入一个整数 T（1 ≤ T ≤ 10⁴），表示测试数据组数。对于每组测试数据：仅有的一行输入两个整数 n 和 m（1 ≤ n ≤ 1014，0 ≤ m < n）。保证最多有 10 组测试数据满足 n 大于 108。"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "key": "output",
        "title": "输出格式",
        "blocks": [
          {
            "kind": "paragraph",
            "text": "每组测试数据输出一行，包含一个整数，表示答案对 998244353 取模的结果。"
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
  },
